content: It will cost 10.000.000 for Brazilians poor taxes payers. The city should be embarrassed to use this kind of money to pay for a Madona show while we don’t have basic sanitation and the people are dying with Dengue and chikungunya virus from mosquitoes. Shame!!! Shame!!! Shame!!!
